         <t:abstract>
            <t:p>Baralām wa-Yǝwāsǝf is a religious romance deriving from the traditional biography of <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS2933Buddha">Buddha</t:persName>.</t:p>
            <t:p>
