         <t:div type="edition">
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="inscription expanded title embedded" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="ExpandedTitle">
               <t:note>The following title is taken from <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet140">Paris, Bibliothèque nationale de France, BnF Éthiopien 140</t:ref>.</t:note>
               <t:ab>
                  በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ መሓሪ፡ ወመስተሣህል፡
                  ወቦቱ፡ ረድኤትነ፤ ንቀድም፡ በረድኤተ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ወስነ፡ ስርሐቱ፡ በጽሒፈ፡ ዜና፡ ዘትበቍዕ፡ ለነፍስ፡ ወለሥጋ፡
                  ዘአምጽእዋ፡ እምሀገረ፡ ህንድ፡ እስከ፡ ቤተ፡ መቅደስ፡ ወጸሐፋ፡ ፩፡ መነኮስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ዘእምጌቴሴማኒ፡ ዘስሙ፡ ዮሐንስ፡
                  በረከተ፡ ጸሎቱ፡ ወትንብልናሁ፡ ተሀሉ፡ ምስለ፡ ንጉሥነ፡ <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5617IyasuII">
                     <t:certainty locus="value" match=".../@ref" cert="unknown"/>ኢያሱ፡</t:persName>
                  ወምስለ፡ ፍቁሩ፡ <t:persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11290Ebeselom">ኤቤሴሎም፡</t:persName> ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡
                  አሜን።
               </t:ab>
            </t:div>
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="inscription expanded title embedded" xml:lang="en" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1199Barala#ExpandedTitle">
               <t:note>The following title is taken from <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet140">Paris, Bibliothèque nationale de France, BnF Éthiopien 140</t:ref>.</t:note>
               <t:ab>
                  In the name of God, the merciful and compassionate, in whom our aid is,
                  we begin with the help of God and with his graceful generosity with the writing of a profitable story for the soul and body, which was brought from India to Jerusalem and
                  was written by a holy monk from Gethsemane, by the name of Yoḥannǝs.
                  May the blessing of his prayer and intercession be with our king <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5617IyasuII">ʾIyāsu</t:persName>
                  and his beloved <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11290Ebeselom">ʾEbeselom</t:persName>.
               </t:ab>
            </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
               <t:ab>
                  ይቤ፡ ሐዋርያ፡ ወንጌላዊ፡ እስመ፡ ኵሎሙ፡ እለ፡ ይገብሩ፡ ግብረ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ እሙንቱ፡ ውሉደ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡
               </t:ab>
            </t:div>
         </t:div>
      </t:body>
   </t:text></TEI>